# Design System — Parc Ganuenta

**Style direction:** Rust, luxe, licht — generous whitespace, refined typography, accent colours used sparingly.

## Font

Two typefaces via Adobe Fonts (Typekit) — both must be in the same kit on fonts.adobe.com.

| Token | Font | Role |
|---|---|---|
| `--font-display` | `forma-djr-display` | Headings — h1 through h6 |
| `--font-sans` | `azo-sans-web` | Body, UI, buttons |

Kit ID placeholder: `YOUR_KIT_ID` — replace in `app/layout.tsx` with the live kit ID.

- `--font-display` is set on `h1–h6` via `@layer base` in `globals.css`
- `--font-sans` is set on `body` and buttons

## Colour Palette

| Token (Tailwind)       | Hex       | Role                              |
|------------------------|-----------|-----------------------------------|
| `brand-stone`          | `#676159` | Primary — headings, nav, borders  |
| `brand-taupe`          | `#CC9A8E` | Secondary — soft decorative use   |
| `brand-pacific`        | `#00ADBC` | Accent — CTAs, links, rules       |
| `brand-sky`            | `#74C4D6` | Soft accent — hover states, icons |
| `brand-cinnamon`       | `#9E6950` | Warm depth — highlights, dividers |
| `brand-dust`           | `#D2D1D1` | Neutral — borders, input strokes  |
| `brand-shadow`         | `#231F20` | Text / high contrast              |
| `brand-platinum`       | `#F0F0F0` | Section backgrounds               |
| `brand-white`          | `#FFFFFF` | Page background / whitespace      |

## Usage Rules

- **Background:** `brand-white` (default), `brand-platinum` for alternating sections
- **Text:** `brand-shadow` for headings/body, `brand-stone` for secondary/muted text
- **Accent sparingly:** `brand-pacific` only for CTAs, active states, and decorative rules
- **Warm accents:** `brand-cinnamon` and `brand-taupe` for highlights, never as large backgrounds
- **Never use felle kleuren on large areas** — accents are stroke, icon, or CTA only

## Buttons

Use the global utility classes from `globals.css`:

```tsx
// Primary — Stone
<button className="btn btn-primary">Meer informatie</button>

// Accent — Pacific Blue
<button className="btn btn-accent">Contact opnemen</button>

// Ghost outlined — Stone
<button className="btn btn-ghost">Bekijk project</button>
```

## Typography Patterns

```tsx
// Section label (all caps, wide tracking)
<p className="label-style">Wonen in Zeeland</p>

// Heading with Pacific Blue rule underneath
<h2 className="heading-rule">Ontdek Parc Ganuenta</h2>

// Centered heading with rule
<h2 className="heading-rule heading-rule-centered text-center">Over ons</h2>
```

## Section Layout

```tsx
<section className="section-padding bg-brand-platinum">
  <div className="container-site">
    {/* content */}
  </div>
</section>
```

## JS Token Reference

For OG images, canvas, or inline SVG — import from `lib/design-system.ts`:

```ts
import { colors, semanticColors, tw } from '@/lib/design-system'
colors.brandPacific   // '#00ADBC'
semanticColors.accent // '#00ADBC'
tw.bgPlatinum         // 'bg-brand-platinum'
```
